profile:
Hello. Thanks for looking. :)

I do General Renovations, Installations, and Repairs. Free Quotes. Labour - $45/hour. 
Fully Insured, Licensed  and WorkSafe(WCB) covered. 
Deposit required for large material purchases (over $500, incl. 10% handling)
No job too small. Any room, any job. I have many years of experience at practically every home repair or renovation job. Drywall, plumbing, electrical, construction, modifications, windows, doors, or just hang a picture or mirror. The list is very long.
I access qualified Tradesmen for specialty tasks (ie: bigger plumbing or electrical jobs). I am your experienced voice to get it done right. 
I am the General Contractor on larger projects, to assist you on getting the right people on the right jobs, with the right materials. General Contractor rate of $60 per hour, plus 10% of all sub-contractors invoices. Balanced with my regular rate of $45 per hour for my labour.

Strata, Commercial, Home or Business Maintenance. 

Delivery Services - My utility trailer, dolly and myself can transport your material, debris, appliances, furniture, or what-have-you. 

Debris clean-up and yard work - Free quotes or pay as it goes.

So, if you want integrity, reliability and good old fashioned honesty then give me a call. My personal mobile number is 604-483-1546.  (Note: Any calls from outside Canada will not be answered due to the volume of US telemarketer calls. Please leave a message and I will call you back.)

I look forward in seeing you soon,
Doug.
